The J2EEDependenciesPage NPE is fixed in 1.0.3 and 1.5 (139832) - re: the EARArtifaceEdit.getModuleURI() NPE, the implementation of that method has significantly changed from 1.0.3 to 1.5 - so, that particular NPE is likely not a problem anymore; if VirtualReference.referencedComponent is ever null, you will get an NPE - Chuck, sending you way for a look.
upping priority for comment. Would be nice to confirm this one is fixed (or not).
